item.description: items: - title: Research Assistant company: College of Science and Engineering, University of Minnesota company_url: ’' company_logo: umngold location: Minneapolis, MN, USA date_start: ‘2024-06-01’ date_end: description: |2- * Collaborated on robotic surgery for histotripsy using the UR5e robotic arm with ROS2 and MoveIt2 in Python. * Mapped singular configurations in C-space to improve motion planning. * Developed path-planning algorithms for constrained and unconstrained trajectories, ensuring collision avoidance in an aquatic environment.
